New Records: Fans ate 49,331 Loonie Dogs, bringing the final season figure to 727,819 — a new record.
Key Match Events: The Red Sox won Tuesday’s game 6-5.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Tuesday’s home game against the Boston Red Sox marked the last 'Loonie Dog' night of the year.
The most Loonie Dogs sold at a game this year was 71,391 on Aug. 6 against Baltimore Orioles.
The most ever consumed in one game was 76,627 on Aug. 28, 2023 against the Washington Nationals.
